Author: mottyl
Content:
Hi everyone 👋 

🎺 The Braavos wallet extension is available on the Chrome Store and is live on Starknet testnet 🎺 

Users can create accounts, connect to dApps, manage tokens and see their NFT collections inside the wallet 💥 

We have been building Braavos with developers in mind 🛠️ 
Developers can use the wallet in `headless mode` in order to auto-test their dApp - See details here [1].
In addition, we have released the `get-starknet-wallet` library that is compatible with the current getStarknet() API but is able to support multiple wallets on StarkNet - see details here [2]

We are here to help with any issue and will be happy if you reach out! 🤝 

[1] - https://braavos.notion.site/Headless-Wallet-and-Using-Devnet-with-Braavos-2072e6fd89fc43158c0239d6baa2f00c
[2] - https://github.com/myBraavos/get-starknet-wallet

Author: laurip
Content: oh, sounds great! What's your take on account contracts - do you auto-deploy one for the user? If yes, what kind of functionality does it have

Author: mottyl
Content:
Hi @LauriP 👋 

Yes, we auto deploy a contract for each account in your wallet. 
It will support all the functionality you know from classic smart-contract base wallets - social recovery, account segmentation, guardians, etc. Plus, a few new surprises we will present closer to mainnet launch.
Source code will be published in the near future.
 
If you want to experience it, you can download and take a look here: <https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/braavos-wallet/jnlgamecbpmbajjfhmmmlhejkemejdma>

Will be happy to get any feedback 🙏

Author: laurip
Content:
Thanks, will definitely have a try.
What about custom account contracts? Do you allow user to switch to one? If not now, is it planned?

Author: mottyl
Content: Not currently. Need to think if it makes sense, as at least some of the IF functionality relates to the capabilities of the contract (might make sense to have a "basic" mode). But if there will be a demand we will definitely consider.

Author: laurip
Content:
understood 🙂 and I agree it's not a trivial thing to do. if you never allow it, you will have problems integrating new innovative account contract features in your wallet, since you'd need to custom-code support for every one of them.
I expect custom account contracts to be a thing in near future. Or at least the possibility for users to incorporate new features in the used account contract, in some fashion

Author: mottyl
Content:
Interesting... 🤔 
Need to think it through 😀

Author: bitmin| Sui Global#6190
Content: hi i install plugin of braavos in my chrome browser but when i open it nothing show to me just a white page any one know what should i do?

Author: mottyl
Content: not yet.

Author: mottyl
Content: Currently there is no interoperability between wallets on StarkNet, so you cannot move between one to the other. We, as a community, working to standardize that, so hopefully it will be possible in the future

Author: mottyl
Content: Unlike Ethereum L1, on StarkNet you have account abstraction, so your public key is not your address on chain.

Author: mottyl
Content: Your wallet account manifestation is actually a smart-contract on chain - so you have a smart-contract deployed on testnet and a smart-contract deployed on mainnet. Hence the different addresses. However, please note that Braavos is still not enabled on mainnet.

Author: mottyl
Content:
Basically, almost any project on StarkNet you can test with Braavos (assuming ArgentX is disabled / not installed).

However, the following projects have built-in support for multiple wallets on top of StarkNet - so the experience is much smoother:
- briq - <https://briq.construction/builder>
- Aspect - <https://testnet.aspect.co/>
- MintSquare - <https://mintsquare.io/>
- mySwap - <https://myswap.xyz>
- StarCombo - <https://testnet.starcombo.xyz/>
- Starkgate - <https://goerli.starkgate.starknet.io/>
- web3-starknet-react (and the projects that rely on it: Phi, Yagi, BitmapBox, ...) - <https://github.com/apibara/starknet-react>
- Eykar - <https://eykar.org/>
- Voyager - <https://goerli.voyager.online/>
- TheNinth - <https://ninth.gg/>
- JediSwap (next release, probably later this week) - <https://app.testnet.jediswap.xyz/#/swap>
- Alpha Road (next release) - <https://testnet.app.alpharoad.fi/>
- ZigZag (next release) 

Probably a few more we are unaware of...

Author: danilowhk
Content: Hi, is there any way I can determine which contract account I want to attach to my private,public key pairs?

Author: yogabraavos
Content: Hi @dan , your account contract address is determined, amongst other things, by the public key generated while deploying the account for the first time. In a future version we might support modification of the  public key for an existing address so you will be able to deploy an account and then swap out the public key, but currently this feature is not available.

Author: yogabraavos
Content:
hi @nestor thank you for your report! you indeed uncovered an edge case when recovering the account from 3rd party, two or more times without doing any transactions in between. 
We are in the process releasing a fix to the extension that will allow you to recover your account correctly.

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
New browser extension released! 🔥 

Dear StarkNet frens and all those who manage their funds with Braavos Wallet from their desktop 💻 
here is the news that will please you! 

Since this morning, you can enjoy:

1) Integrated SWAP function - 
😎 Buy your favorite cryptos like ETH, DAI and USDC in 3 clicks directly from your wallet. 
 
2) New navigation menu - 
👈 Enjoy the smooth navigation between your wallet, the "Swap tokens" screen and the NFTs manager. 

3) New applications bar - 
🗺️ Enjoy easy access and immediate visibility to the most important things - Menu, current account address and the network you are running on.

Please open your extensions, try them and share your feedback on the user experience in the channel 💬general .🧐 
We will not stop our efforts until the wallet fits your needs. 

PS: If you don't have the extension yet, you can download it here - https://braavos.app/ 
and direct link to Chrome extension: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/braavos-wallet/jnlgamecbpmbajjfhmmmlhejkemejdma
Enjoy!

For the time being, the only thing I can offer is to use different browsers (or mobile devices) for your Braavos extension/app. 
Adding an account which is not derived from the seed is on the roadmap, but prob won't be supported in the near future.

Author: mottyl
Content:
There is currently no interoperability between wallets on StarkNet. Since both wallets are smart contract wallets that deploy different account contracts on-chain, you get different addresses. 

I suggest that you will create a new Braavos wallet (new seed) and enjoy the full Braavos experience and enhance features. You can use Braavos as an extension on one of the popular browsers, as well as on Android and iOS - <https://braavos.app/download/>

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
Dear Braavos Nation @everyone :braavos: 

One of the most important articles of the beginning of 2023  for the #starknet tech community almost went unnoticed. 🔏 

Published yesterday morning in a heavy flow of tweets, it had also escaped me.
Fortunately, some of you came to tell me about it. 🙏 

This article is the result of a collaboration between StarkWare :StarkNet: and Braavos :braavos: .
The article aimed to demonstrate how Account Abstraction allows wallets to meet (and exceed) the UX expectations of Web2 users and how Braavos harnessed this capability to introduce the Hardware Signer.

Whether you're a techie or not, a degen or an investor, this article is a must-read to understand how the Hardware Signer, and Braavos Wallet, is a game changers in the crypto world.

If you see this message, rejoice: you are early in the Braavos long adventure!

📣  Please share and amplify massively:

1 - For those who do not participate in our community program, here is the tweet to access the article:
 📑 https://twitter.com/StarkWareLtd/status/1614986112904355840

2 - A flash mission is waiting for you to celebrate our collaboration!
:lightningbolt: https://braavos.crew3.xyz/questboard/232a4918-260b-49bf-aa1b-d5c67a3ee79f

3 - Join our next community call to meet Motty, the article co-author to understand the potential of the AA and how it is used with the Hardware Signer: 
👥 https://discord.com/events/962985965889142844/1050475780037160960

Please share your feedback or questions in the general channel 😀

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
📢 Account Abstraction Security Pyramid announcement  at the StarkWare Sessions 2023 📢 

Hi @everyone 

Motty is out of stage where he presented the Braavos new security concept that strikes a balance between high levels of protection & ease of adoption. 
It have been designed to ensure a seamless experience.

In few words, we added the Multi-Signer (3FA) on top of the Hardware Signer (2FA). 

What does it means for you, as Braavos Wallet users?
It means that, with the 3FA, you are using the wallet that offers the highest level of security, while being able to customize it for each of your accounts.

Please give ❤️  and share 🔁  the good news.
Here is the official public announcement: https://twitter.com/myBraavos/status/1622548536444305411?s=20&t=MNnIwZKO0__xex2zNATqzg

The new wallet version is actually being tested by our official testers. 
So it will be released to you in the next couple of days!

Note that we will discuss thsi topic on Thursday during our Community Call. 
Please set your reminder! 
https://discord.com/events/962985965889142844/1050475893396607037

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
The Multi-Signer  🥁🥁🥁🥁🥁

The Multi-Signer adds additional layer of security on top of the Hardware / Protected Signer by securing your account with 2 keys from 2 different devices for ultimate security 🔐

You can enjoy 3-Factor-Authentication (3FA):
- something you know 📝
- something you have 📱
- something you are 👤
without the need for an additional seed phrase! 🔥

How to setup (on a Goerli Tetnet account)?
    1. On your browser Extension go to Account Settings -> Account Security and select Multi-Singer. You will see a QR code.
    2. Open your Braavos mobile app, scan the QR code and follow the instruction to sign the Multi-Signer setup transaction.

That's it! 💫

The new version 3.6.5 is avail on Google Chrome Store, Android Play Store and on the App Store.
https://braavos.app/download/

Try it out! 🚀 
We will be happy to get your feedbacks 🙏

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
🔥 🔥 🔥 Hi @everyone 🔥 🔥 🔥 

We are excited to announce that Stage 2 of the "The Braavos Helmets" campaign is now open! 🎉

In this stage, you can win an "OG#3" role and one of the 10 exclusive "Whisperer Helmet - Level 2" NFTs. 
The goal is to reward members of our community who reach the Whisperer level by completing missions in our Crew3 community program. 

Each participant will be able to unlock the OG#3 role, and 10 of them will be randomly selected to win one of the 10 exclusive NFTs.🎁

To participate, you will need to:
1 - Complete simple missions of the Braavos Community Program to unlock the "Whisperer of Braavos" role. You can do this by collecting 500XP. Access the missions here: https://crew3.xyz/c/braavos/questboard

2 - Once you have acquired the "Whisperer of Braavos" role, you can access the "#Helmet NFT Campaign" quest, claim your OG#3 role, and register for the random draw. 

Community members with the Whisperer role or above can go directly to the "#Helmet NFT Campaign" quest.

The conditions are simple 📝
- Provide the address of your Bravo Wallet account in your profile. Note that to qualify, your account must be deployed on-chain.
- Unlock and claim the “Whisperer of Braavos” role https://crew3.xyz/c/braavos/questboard/2e1a9301-14da-4430-9ae0-b617e1c379f4

The campaign will end on February 28th at midnight. 
The winners will be drawn the next day.🗓️

You can learn more about the community program in 👥⎪community-program channel
And get support join the " 🦸⎢support-roles-crew3 channel

We wish you all good luck, and don't forget to 🔁  this news with your community!🤞

PS: Don't forget that you can still participate in Stage 1 and win one of the 100 "Braavosian Helmet - Level 1” NFTs: 
https://discord.com/channels/962985965889142844/964080302957920287/1074980133846388776

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
No, the account upgrade is not the same as a wallet update. 
Indeed, you now enjoy the V3.8.0 for the client side/ the app/ the extension.

But it can be that your accounts, what is link to the smart contract is not upgraded.

So please check all your accounts ( mainnet + testnet) and if you see the blue banner, click on it please.

CC @Wind Rider | StarkTitan @scarlet(σ, σ) | StarkTitan There is confusion between "Wallet Update" and "Account Upgrade". We need the account to be upgraded to avoid loosing funds.

Author: Bertrand I Braavos#2725
Content:
Dear StarkNet Enthusiasts,

Get Ready for a Stellar Experience: v3.10.0 is Here! 🌠

We're over the moon to announce that v3.10.0 is now available in the Chrome store! 🚀

Prepare for liftoff as the dApps gallery now featuring a sleek full screen mode! 🌌 
To access this cosmic upgrade, simply navigate to the dApps tab in your wallet and click the expand icon in the top-left corner.

In full screen mode, you'll gain access to a galaxy of information, including:

- The total number of dApps you've engaged with 🌐
- A record of your interactions with each dApp 📊
- A comprehensive overview of your transactions over time ⏳
- Your awe-inspiring Starknet Pro score 🏆

Blast off and explore the new dApps gallery now! ✨ Don't forget to share your thoughts and feedback with us here on Discord. We can't wait to hear what you think of this stellar update! 🌟

To try Braavos, download your favorite extension and mobile version of the wallet here: https://braavos.app/download-braavos-wallet/

Content:
Contrary to what they said above, it is possible for you to migrate Argent X to Braavos, as well as Braavos to Argent X.

For this, you just need to insert your seed as if you were going to recover your wallet.

When you open Argent X, you have the option to restore your wallet. Then you put the Braavos seed and that's it
